## Why MPL-2.0 for this repo?

`convergio-design` is the Convergio design system. We want it to be
adopted as widely as possible — by solopreneurs, agencies, companies,
open source projects, everyone.

MPL-2.0 gives you maximum freedom: use it, modify it, ship it.
The only requirement is that changes to MPL-licensed files stay open.

The rest of the Convergio ecosystem uses the
[Convergio Community License](https://github.com/Roberdan/convergio/blob/main/LICENSE).

